<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#E45649;--shiki-dark:#E06C75">space-between</span><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD">：与交叉轴两端对齐，轴线之间的间隔平均分布。</span></span>
